headline: AIZ Q4 Deep Dive: Home Warranty Launch and Housing Growth Drive Mixed Market Reaction
summary: Insurance services company Assurant (NYSE:AIZ) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 7.9% year on year to $3.35 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $5.61 per share was 1.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
